	HOME & BUSINESS 






	THE DYNEGY DIFFERENCE







EMPOWERING YOU TO MAKE SMART ELECTRIC SUPPLY CHOICES.
At Dynegy, we’re more than just one of the largest retail suppliers of electricity. We can also generate more than 26,000 megawatts of power. With our experience and in-depth energy industry knowledge, we pride ourselves on delivering smart energy solutions to all our customers. 
Through our retail suppliers, Dynegy Retail and Homefield Energy we currently serve  thousands of homes and businesses throughout Illinois and Ohio. Find out today what we can do for you.








 

